# Local-only secrets and operator notes — never commit
SECURITY-NOTES.local.md
settings.local.json
**/SECURITY-NOTES.local.md
**/settings.local.json

# Prevent recursive .cursor nesting (e.g. .cursor/.cursor/...) created when an
# external tool or hook writes runtime state with the wrong working directory.
# The canonical hub is this folder; there must never be a .cursor inside it.
/.cursor/

# Generated by `cursor-hub export` (rules-md, copilot-instructions, etc.).
# Regenerate locally; not part of the tracked hub baseline (same policy as root /.github/* exports).
/dist/
